{"word":"G824 - ἄτοπος - átopos - at'-op-os - Amiss","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄτοπος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">átopos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">at'-op-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Amiss</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தகாத, சேதமான, பொல்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"out of place; not befitting, unbecoming, improper, wicked, inconvenient, harmful"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G5117 - τόπος - tópos - top'-os/5117\">G5117</a>; <i>out of place</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>improper</i>, <i>injurious</i>, <i>wicked:</i> - amiss, harm, unreasonable.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}